### Register Student
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "student1",
  "lastName": "",
  "email": "student1@mail.com",
  "role": "STUDENT",
  "password": "student1",
  "profileImageUrl": "https://example.com/avatars/user.png"
}

### Student Login
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student1@mail.com",
  "password": "student1"
}

### Daily quote
GET http://localhost:4000/auth/daily-quote

### Read counselors
GET http://localhost:4000/student-api/counselors

### Read wellness articles
GET http://localhost:4000/student-api/articles

### Create anonymous post
POST http://localhost:4000/forum-api/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "feeling": "STRESSED",
  "content": "I feel mentally exhausted because of academic pressure."
}

### Read forum posts
GET http://localhost:4000/forum-api/posts

### Add comment
PUT http://localhost:4000/forum-api/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": "6a126ea98dc9b4af5fc36695",
  "comment": "You are not alone. Many students feel this during difficult times."
}

### Support post
PATCH http://localhost:4000/forum-api/support
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": "6a126ea98dc9b4af5fc36695"
}

### Report content
POST http://localhost:4000/forum-api/reports
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "POST",
  "post": "6a126ea98dc9b4af5fc36695",
  "reason": "Harmful content"
}

### Request counselor
POST http://localhost:4000/student-api/chat-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "counselor": "6a0f2573ca44eee838599d06",
  "message": "I want to talk privately."
}

### Complete meditation
POST http://localhost:4000/meditation-api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionType": "DEEP_BREATHING",
  "durationInMinutes": 10
}

### Meditation stats
GET http://localhost:4000/meditation-api/stats

### Mood check-in
PUT http://localhost:4000/student-api/mood
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mood": "CALM",
  "note": "Feeling better after breathing."
}

### AI Saathi
POST http://localhost:4000/ai-saathi-api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Can you suggest calming songs?I want hindi songs"
}

### Notifications
GET http://localhost:4000/notification-api/notifications
